 and multi-factor association is allowed.\nClusters are respectively anchored by the pure variables, and form overlapping\nsub-groups of the p-dimensional random vector X. The Latent model approach to\nOVErlapping clustering is reflected in the name of our algorithm, LOVE.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 23 Apr 2017 20:43:44 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 28 Sep 2017 04:06:07 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 22 Mar 2018 03:01:20 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 20 Jun 2019 23:02:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-06-24"}
