bly less sensitive to the correlated noise, and can\nachieve a better sensitivity to the stochastic GW signal in the most\npessimistic case.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 24 Apr 2017 08:38:17 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 14 Jul 2017 05:57:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-07-19"}
