ude textured polarization states and\nunusual forms of superconductivity that remain to be understood theoretically.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 24 Apr 2017 14:56:25 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 10 Nov 2017 20:12:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-11-15"}
